title: Lichen-Covered Rock
description: A close-up view of a rock surface adorned with bright orange and yellow lichen, set against a clear blue sky. The rock has a rugged texture, and the lichen adds a vibrant contrast to the natural stone.

title: Underwater Scene with Turtle
description: An underwater scene featuring a sea turtle swimming gracefully above a vibrant coral reef. The reef is teeming with colorful fish, including yellow and striped species, and a jellyfish is visible in the foreground. The water is clear, showcasing the rich blues and the diverse marine life.

title: Coastal Landscape
description: A picturesque coastal scene featuring golden cliffs rising from a turquoise sea. The foreground is adorned with vibrant pink flowers, adding a splash of color to the serene beach setting. The sky is clear with a few fluffy clouds, creating a tranquil atmosphere.

title: Snow-Capped Mountain Peak
description: A close-up view of a rugged mountain peak, partially covered in snow, against a clear blue sky. The rocky texture of the mountain is visible, showcasing its natural formations and the contrast between the snow and the rocky surfaces.
